{"tid":352582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"橫頭磡邨血案　36歲繼子斬傷37歲後父","createTime":"2017-08-09T01:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T04:39:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b7cccadce3f23492a5951ed270c73961f4e7f5c","tid":352582,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170809/large/1502223099_ab67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170809%2Flarge%2F1502223099_ab67.jpg&h=a2c617ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙橫頭磡邨宏亮樓，一名姓潘37歲內地男子，與50多歲本地妻子，以及妻子與前夫所生的36歲兒子，住在一個單位。凌晨2時許，潘正在熟睡中，繼子突然失常，持菜刀及生果刀向他襲擊，他兩邊肩膊中刀受傷，負傷跑落地下大堂，向保安員求救。<br />\n<br />\n繼子傷人後棄刀逃去，救護員到場將傷者送院；警方持盾牌搜捕未有發現。現場消息指，繼子有精神病記錄，身高約1.7米、肥身材、蓄短黑髮，案發時身穿灰白色粗橫間條上衣，黑色短運動褲，螢光橙色褲腳及褲骨，黑色拖鞋。"},{"pid":"17198fd574451f97f6fc05393744228504e18121","tid":352582,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:04:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57058576&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57058576%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170809&d=hiO3DfHFJ8tI%2BuOtwDxSdk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4d328b8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57058576%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170809&h=110179dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57058576&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170809</a>"},{"pid":"93540bedb67751d43d42dcc919ec7ea59d965306","tid":352582,"uid":23295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:06:19.000Z","msg":"50路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p